{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-archived-blog-template-js","path":"/2014/12/qq-animation-project-2/","result":{"data":{"archivedBlogPostJson":{"categories":[{"path":"/category/film/","name":"独立电影与短片"}],"tags":[{"name":"CG","path":"/tag/cg/"},{"name":"Maya","path":"/tag/maya/"},{"name":"QQ","path":"/tag/qq/"},{"name":"动画","path":"/tag/animation/"},{"name":"愚人节","path":"/tag/april-fools-day/"},{"name":"玩笑","path":"/tag/joke/"},{"name":"短片","path":"/tag/short-film/"}],"featured_media":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"fixed","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/3720d82b088595e01d64a1621802a5de/e737e/renderTest-2-0-00-00-001.jpg","srcSet":"/static/3720d82b088595e01d64a1621802a5de/e737e/renderTest-2-0-00-00-001.jpg 800w","sizes":"800px"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/3720d82b088595e01d64a1621802a5de/e7773/renderTest-2-0-00-00-001.webp 800w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"800px"}]},"width":800,"height":400}}},"path":"/2014/12/qq-animation-project-2/","date":"2014-12-05T15:57:22.000Z","excerpt":"最初准备采用xGen来生成基本体毛发，可反复检查始终无法让渲染结果稳定，偶尔会出现毛发颜色错误的故障，估计是软 … ","title":"Q仔动画愚人节项目2——毛发的修改、渲染与合成测试","content":"<p><figure id=\"attachment_1632\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1632\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/QQ.6.81.1080HD.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-1632 size-full\" src=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/QQ.6.81.1080HD.jpg\" alt=\"QQ角色渲染测试，使用xGen生成毛发\" srcset=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/QQ.6.81.1080HD.jpg 1920w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/QQ.6.81.1080HD-300x168.jpg 300w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/QQ.6.81.1080HD-1024x576.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 89vw, (max-width: 1000px) 54vw, (max-width: 1071px) 543px, 580px\" /></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1632\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">QQ角色渲染测试，使用xGen生成毛发，volume fur</figcaption></figure></p>\n<p>最初准备采用xGen来生成基本体毛发，可反复检查始终无法让渲染结果稳定，偶尔会出现毛发颜色错误的故障，估计是软件故障，且缓慢的渲染速度无法接受，最后还是换用Fur插件。</p>\n<p><figure id=\"attachment_1655\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1655\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/renderTest-2-0-00-00-001.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-1655 size-full\" src=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/renderTest-2-0-00-00-001.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/renderTest-2-0-00-00-001.jpg 1366w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/renderTest-2-0-00-00-001-300x168.jpg 300w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/renderTest-2-0-00-00-001-1024x576.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 89vw, (max-width: 1000px) 54vw, (max-width: 1071px) 543px, 580px\" /></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1655\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">QQ渲染与合成测试，使用Fur Plugin</figcaption></figure></p>\n<p>使用Fur插件重制毛发之后，渲染速度快了很多，将mental ray渲染的indirect、diffuseNoShadow、specular、relflection通道和AO层合成到照片场景中测试了一下，与下图Q仔照片相比较，几乎达到预想的效果，还需要一些灯光与毛发属性的修改，在实际动画场景渲染中再做微调。</p>\n<p><figure id=\"attachment_1651\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1651\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/IMG_20141202_163224.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-1651\" src=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/IMG_20141202_163224.jpg\" alt=\"Q仔玩偶的实拍照片\" srcset=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/IMG_20141202_163224.jpg 1366w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/IMG_20141202_163224-300x168.jpg 300w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/IMG_20141202_163224-1024x576.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 89vw, (max-width: 1000px) 54vw, (max-width: 1071px) 543px, 580px\" /></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1651\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Q仔玩偶的实拍照片</figcaption></figure></p>\n<p>下面是时候开始研究下这个短片的故事本身了！</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2014/12/qq-animation-project-2/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2727970573","3709504828","4110059069"],"slicesMap":{}}